title: Sankey Visualizer
description:
This scenario simulates data ingestion from various sources such as FortiSIEM, FortiNDR, FortiManager, and FortiAnalyzer to demonstrate the usage of the 'SOC Overview Sankey' widget.

Observe the following

* Demo Alert and incident records are created
* The SOC Alert Flow (Sankey) dashboard visualizes the flow of data across generated alerts and escalated incidents, as shown in the screenshot below
